dc_title_s: Central America, Mexico--east coast, Isla Cozumel (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: National Imagery and Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by hachures. "From a Mexican chart of 1984." "Copyright restrictions of the country of origin continue to exist." "Source listing Mexican chart 925." "Soundings in meters." Includes tidal information. Georeferenced nautical chart.
